unified-package-manager (1.0.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of Unified Package Manager
  * Unified search across APT, Snap, and Flatpak repositories
  * One-click installation and uninstallation of packages
  * Settings panel with repository toggles and preferences
  * Comprehensive logging system with export functionality
  * Real-time in-app notifications for all operations
  * SQLite database for tracking installed apps and user preferences
  * Support for custom APT repositories (PPAs)
  * Automatic Flathub repository setup
  * Package filtering by repository type
  * PyQt5-based graphical user interface
  * Security features with pkexec privilege escalation
  * Multi-language desktop entry support
  * Professional application icon
  * Comprehensive documentation and troubleshooting guide

 -- Zorin App Organizer Team <support@zorinos.com>  Tue, 18 Nov 2025 12:00:00 +0000
